				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: HP or AC?<a name="63802"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Sep 23 04 10:56 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>What I have always understood is that ac is good upto a point and then its benefits are reduced.  This point depends upon the ATK of the mobs you fight.  This &quot;soft cap&quot; has changed as the expansions were released - somewhere in these forums someone has listed them but it is like 1000 for original norrath, 1200 for kunark, 1600 for luclin and 2000 for pop.
<br />

<br />
You can see from my magelo that I'm mostly in baz gear (some purchased and some given) and I dont raid.  I dont seem to be able to get my AC much above 1k.  Does anyone have any suggestions?  I know there are some obvious upgrade points (the gob ring for instance) but any suggestions would be helpful.
